    "longBusinessSummary": "Innovative Technology Development Corporation provides technology solutions in Vietnam and internationally. It offers smart traffic, smart industrial park, automatic toll collection, integrated security, emergency management, and other solutions and products for telecommunication and informatic fields; and energy infrastructure solutions, including anti-lightning, precision air conditioning, and solar energy systems, as well as power and UPS, and data center solutions; and mechanical and electrical solutions for buildings and factories. The company also provides electrical system design and installation services; integrated electrical and automation solutions; system maintenance solutions; and training courses for industrial automation systems, as well as supplies equipment for electrical automation. In addition, it offers software development, API and system integration, software quality control, and software deployment services; and customer loyalty, building digital culture, and decentralized application development solutions. Further, the company engages in trading of CCTV, burglar alarms, industrial, civil measure device; electronic and telecommunications equipment, as well as spare parts. Innovative Technology Development Corporation was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
